title: How to prepare for Mars? NASA consults Navy sub force
text: How to prepare for Mars? NASA consults Navy sub force By Associated Press | October 4, 2015 @ 9:36 pm This Nov. 15, 2013 photo released by NASA shows the three-story Human Exploration Research Analog habitat at the Johnson Space Center in Houston. The space agency, which is contemplating a future journey to Mars, is working with a military laboratory at the submarine base in Groton, Conn., to measure how teams handle stress during month-long simulations of space flight. (Bill Stafford/NASA via AP)
